Package: indecr
Title: Access Argentine Socioeconomic Data from Public APIs
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Lisandro", "Seghezzo Prieri", , "seghezzoprieri@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides functions to download, chain, and analyze official
    Argentine time series including CPI, wages, exchange rates, and
    poverty indicators from INDEC and BCRA public APIs.
